  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and saut\u00e9 until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in garlic, tomato paste, balsamic vinegar, and water. Bring to a simmer.",
    "Add cumin seeds, coriander powder, paprika, and salt. Simmer for another 2-3 minutes.",
    "Increase heat to high, add chopped olives, and stir well.",
    "Cook for an additional 5 minutes until the sauce has thickened slightly and olives are heated through.",
    "Stir in fresh parsley and serve hot over toast or a wrap."
